trans-unit.source: Represents a container for <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3D"></xref> objects.
The <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.ContainerUIElement3D.Children%2A> collection of a ContainerUIElement3D element can only consist of <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> objects.
Adding a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> child to a ContainerUIElement3D implicitly adds it to the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3DCollection> for the ContainerUIElement3D element.
trans-unit.target: Hozzáadása egy <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>egy ContainerUIElement3D gyermeke implicit módon hozzáadja azt a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3DCollection>ContainerUIElement3D elemhez.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3DCollection> </xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>

trans-unit.source: ContainerUIElement3D does not have a visual representation; it serves as a container for other visual 3-D objects.
trans-unit.target: ContainerUIElement3D nem rendelkezik a visual megjelenítése; más visual 3D objektumok tárolására szolgál.

trans-unit.source: ContainerUIElement3D is a <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D> object, which provides support for input, focus, and events in 3-D.
trans-unit.target: ContainerUIElement3D van egy <xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>objektum, amely támogatja a beviteli fókuszt és 3-D események.</xref:System.Windows.UIElement3D>

trans-unit.source: This class does not set the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3D.Visual3DModel%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Ez az osztály nem állítja be a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3D.Visual3DModel%2A>tulajdonság.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Visual3D.Visual3DModel%2A>
